Invocation Name: seattle bridges
des:
Seattle Bridges is a Skill that lets daily commuters know the status of their local draw bridge before they start their commute.
The draw bridges that will be monitored are:
 -Ballard Bridge -Fremont Bridge
 -University Bridge -Montlake Bridge
 -SW Spokane Bridge - South Park Bridge
 -First Ave S Bridge
